    <description>Chain mail forged with an ancient design that provides above average physical defense. The design of the armor includes a symmetrical etching of arcane runes that bestow the wearer with enhanced power. Once crafted, these runes will attract an ancient spirit to embody the mail and grants the wearer a chance to cause additional arcane damage following any attack; however, this comes at a price - all abilities will require more energy to use (this cannot be overwritten), and the bearer is beset with nightmares that slowly break down mental resistances.
	
